    href="../../xincludes/scrollkeeper-dir.xml"/>

    <para><parameter>--prefix=$(pkg-config
    --variable=prefix gnome-doc-utils)</parameter>:
    This rebuilds the <filename>Makefile</filename>s with the same prefix as
